# Applies to BOTH image builds: docker-compose.yml builds backend/Dockerfile
# and frontend/Dockerfile with the repo root as context (npm workspaces —
# the shared package-lock.json lives here). Keeping node_modules & friends out
# of the context matters both for speed and for correctness: locally installed
# node_modules contain native binaries (sharp, bcrypt) for the HOST platform
# and must never leak into an image.
.git
.claude
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
backend/uploads
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
docs
**/*.md
docker-compose.yml
